.DT
enter_exit_mess
$MUDNAME$ Creator Help
enter_exit_mess

.SH Name
.SP 5 5
enter_exit_mess -  This method is called when an object leaves or arrives in the room.
.EP

.SH Syntax
.SI 5
void enter_exit_mess(string mess,
object thing,
int going)
.EI

.SH Parameters
.SI 5
%^BOLD%^mess%^RESET%^ - the message to print
%^BOLD%^thing%^RESET%^ - the thing which is leaving/arriving
%^BOLD%^going%^RESET%^ - if it is going

.EI

.SH Defined in
.SI 5
/global/player/events.c
.EI

.SH Description
.SP 5 5

This method is called when an object leaves or arrives in
the room.  It prints out
the message, well adds it to the queue of printable messages.
.EP

